    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You have set your <code>%JAVA_HOME</code> to jdk 1.7, but you are trying to compile using 1.8. Install jdk 1.8 and make sure your <code>%JAVA_HOME</code> points to that or drop the target release to 1.7. </p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>invalid target release: 1.8</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>The target release refers to the jdk version.</p>\n"
  }, {
