    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>In my case the maven \"Run configuration\" was using the wrong JRE (1.7). Be sure to check <strong>Run -> Run Configurations -> (Tab) JRE</strong> to be some jdk1.8.x.</p>\n"
