    "question_id" : 28291691,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The issue was resolved as I was having a JDK pointing to 1.7 and JRE pointing to 1.8. Check in the command prompt by typing</p>\n<pre><code>java -version\n</code></pre>\n<p>and</p>\n<pre><code>javac -version\n</code></pre>\n<p>Both should be same.\n </p>\n"
  }, {
