    "answer_id" : 54890789,
    "question_id" : 28291691,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Do a force Maven Update which will bring the compatible 1.8 Jar Versions and then while building, update the JRE Versions in Execute environment to 1.8 from Run Configurations and hit RUN</p>\n"
  }, {
