    "last_activity_date" : 1564990566,
    "creation_date" : 1564990566,
    "answer_id" : 57354107,
    "question_id" : 28291691,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>As mentioned by Camila Macedo - you have to explicitly point the java version for compiler-plugin. For spring boot you can do that by next property:</p>\n\n<pre><code>  &lt;properties&gt;\n    &lt;java.version&gt;1.8&lt;/java.version&gt;\n    &lt;maven.compiler.release&gt;8&lt;/maven.compiler.release&gt;\n  &lt;/properties&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
      "owner" : {
